インタフェース RedisList<E>

  • すべてのスーパーインタフェース:
    java.util.concurrent.BlockingDeque<E>, java.util.concurrent.BlockingQueue<E>, BoundKeyOperations<java.lang.String>, java.util.Collection<E>, java.util.Deque<E>, java.lang.Iterable<E>, java.util.List<E>, java.util.Queue<E>, RedisCollection<E>, RedisStore
    既知の実装クラスのリスト:
    DefaultRedisList

    public interface RedisList<E>
extends RedisCollection<E>, java.util.List<E>, java.util.concurrent.BlockingDeque<E>
    Redis extension for the List contract. Supports List, Queue and Deque contracts as well as their equivalent blocking siblings BlockingDeque and BlockingDeque.
    作成者:
    Costin Leau
